{"meta":{"title":"chenshuohuang的个人博客","subtitle":"subtitle","description":"description","author":"chenshuohuang","url":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"分类","date":"2023-02-08T15:25:49.009Z","updated":"2023-02-08T15:25:49.009Z","comments":false,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"about","date":"2023-02-08T14:58:46.000Z","updated":"2023-02-08T14:58:46.480Z","comments":true,"path":"about/index.html","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/about/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"标签","date":"2023-02-08T15:24:25.490Z","updated":"2023-02-08T15:24:25.490Z","comments":false,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"20230215","slug":"daily/20230215","date":"2023-02-15T15:36:30.000Z","updated":"2023-02-15T15:13:25.945Z","comments":true,"path":"2023/02/15/daily/20230215/","link":"","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/2023/02/15/daily/20230215/","excerpt":"","text":"今晚和大只(朋友)聊了许多，聊了成长、团队管理方面的内容，摘抄了几句，感受一下： 该用行动用行动，对聪明人不用讲得直接，点一下就行～ 用手段&#x2F;行动而不是用语言去带人，这是我最深的感触 成年人没有教育只有筛选 高层和我们最大的不同，一方面是信息不同，位置决定脑袋，但另一方面是信息的处理和我们思维的不同，这就是沙盘推演需要做到的 逻辑就是，沙盘推演，我现在又开始用笔写了，1.2.3.4.5.6 所以 7～回归到最开始的了，沙盘推演，推演事情发展的逻辑，推演形式的变化～到最高层的时候就能推演每个决策对未来的影响 我喜欢马云说的一句话：不会表达不是口才不好，而是没有理出逻辑重点来～ 学着上帝视角，经常用第三人视角看自己～ 经常想对方在乎的以及想要的","categories":[{"name":"成长感悟","slug":"成长感悟","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/categories/%E6%88%90%E9%95%BF%E6%84%9F%E6%82%9F/"}],"tags":[{"name":"人性","slug":"人性","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E4%BA%BA%E6%80%A7/"},{"name":"朋友","slug":"朋友","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B/"},{"name":"聊天","slug":"聊天","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E8%81%8A%E5%A4%A9/"},{"name":"沙盘演练","slug":"沙盘演练","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E6%B2%99%E7%9B%98%E6%BC%94%E7%BB%83/"},{"name":"上帝视角","slug":"上帝视角","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%9D%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%92/"}]},{"title":"20230214","slug":"daily/20230214","date":"2023-02-14T15:36:30.000Z","updated":"2023-02-14T15:15:11.311Z","comments":true,"path":"2023/02/14/daily/20230214/","link":"","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/2023/02/14/daily/20230214/","excerpt":"","text":"今天一天忙于生产问题的复盘和沟通，有收获，不过代价有点大：900 多万的借款本该拒绝而通过了。 收获有： 让业务重视特征变量监控； 发现开发流程上、生产验收流程上的漏洞，通过优化流程机制来保障，将历史输入项跑批验证强制加在发版验证流程中； 认清人为不可控因素，挖掘程序替代人为的验证处理方案。","categories":[{"name":"成长感悟","slug":"成长感悟","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/categories/%E6%88%90%E9%95%BF%E6%84%9F%E6%82%9F/"}],"tags":[{"name":"生产问题","slug":"生产问题","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"}]},{"title":"20230213","slug":"daily/20230213","date":"2023-02-13T15:36:30.000Z","updated":"2023-02-14T15:06:13.355Z","comments":true,"path":"2023/02/13/daily/20230213/","link":"","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/2023/02/13/daily/20230213/","excerpt":"","text":"在生产问题面前就能看出一个人的工作态度。","categories":[{"name":"成长感悟","slug":"成长感悟","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/categories/%E6%88%90%E9%95%BF%E6%84%9F%E6%82%9F/"}],"tags":[{"name":"生产问题","slug":"生产问题","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"}]},{"title":"20230212","slug":"daily/20230212","date":"2023-02-12T15:36:30.000Z","updated":"2023-02-12T15:47:35.698Z","comments":true,"path":"2023/02/12/daily/20230212/","link":"","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/2023/02/12/daily/20230212/","excerpt":"","text":"今晚看书学习到了即兴演讲的一般步骤： 感谢：感谢平台 or 领导 or 其他在场的人提供机会发表言论等等； 自谦：表达自己的思考欠缺、不全面，欢迎大家指正等等； 认同：认同前面发言人的观点； 观点：表达自己的观点。 有时得适当放松一下，比如看看电影、电视剧，今天在回深的高铁上，看了书《秘书工作手记：办公室老江湖的职场心法》，刚开始看着还挺起劲的，后面看着看着精力不足，就看不下去，在换乘地铁时，就看了 2 倍速的《狂飙》，得到了充分的放松。","categories":[{"name":"成长感悟","slug":"成长感悟","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/categories/%E6%88%90%E9%95%BF%E6%84%9F%E6%82%9F/"}],"tags":[{"name":"即兴演讲","slug":"即兴演讲","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E5%8D%B3%E5%85%B4%E6%BC%94%E8%AE%B2/"},{"name":"适当放松","slug":"适当放松","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E9%80%82%E5%BD%93%E6%94%BE%E6%9D%BE/"}]},{"title":"20230211","slug":"daily/20230211","date":"2023-02-11T15:30:30.000Z","updated":"2023-02-11T15:33:52.010Z","comments":true,"path":"2023/02/11/daily/20230211/","link":"","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/2023/02/11/daily/20230211/","excerpt":"","text":"写博客这么多年，一直是从自身出发，写下啥就分享啥，没有定位所以也断断续续地写，无法坚持下来，今晚试着想了下，接下来博客、公众号的定位和受众，初步设定如下。 定位：互联网金融风控技术、产品、业务知识分享以及职场摸爬滚打经验分享。受众：初入职场 5 年以内的互联网金融风控人群。 定位和受众不会一成不变，目前定下的，可能是接下来 3 年甚至只有 1 年的定位和受众，当然也不会随便变动。 设置了定位和受众，那么就有了目标，确切地说，是有了思路。博客范围会广一些，会写一些平时的成长感悟，这定位和受众，更倾向于是应用于公众号。","categories":[{"name":"成长感悟","slug":"成长感悟","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/categories/%E6%88%90%E9%95%BF%E6%84%9F%E6%82%9F/"}],"tags":[{"name":"定位","slug":"定位","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D/"},{"name":"受众","slug":"受众","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E5%8F%97%E4%BC%97/"}]},{"title":"20230210","slug":"daily/20230210","date":"2023-02-10T15:55:30.000Z","updated":"2023-02-10T16:01:19.654Z","comments":true,"path":"2023/02/10/daily/20230210/","link":"","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/2023/02/10/daily/20230210/","excerpt":"","text":"深思慎言：说出去的话要负责任，需要经过深思熟虑，确定可以说出才能说，不轻易说出一些情绪化的话。","categories":[{"name":"成长感悟","slug":"成长感悟","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/categories/%E6%88%90%E9%95%BF%E6%84%9F%E6%82%9F/"}],"tags":[{"name":"深思慎言","slug":"深思慎言","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E6%B7%B1%E6%80%9D%E6%85%8E%E8%A8%80/"}]},{"title":"20230209","slug":"daily/20230209","date":"2023-02-09T15:58:31.000Z","updated":"2023-02-09T16:04:14.108Z","comments":true,"path":"2023/02/09/daily/20230209/","link":"","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/2023/02/09/daily/20230209/","excerpt":"","text":"今天发版日，有如下两点感悟： 在职场，犯错没问题，总会给试错的机会，但是要从犯错中得到成长，要让大家知道你在这个过程中，历练了，如果没有，反而经常犯同样的错，那只会让自己离核心骨干位置越来越远。 技术还是需要历练和积累，方案设计永远没有尽头，只有想与不想。","categories":[{"name":"成长感悟","slug":"成长感悟","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/categories/%E6%88%90%E9%95%BF%E6%84%9F%E6%82%9F/"}],"tags":[{"name":"试错","slug":"试错","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E8%AF%95%E9%94%99/"},{"name":"成长","slug":"成长","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E6%88%90%E9%95%BF/"}]},{"title":"20230208","slug":"daily/20230208","date":"2023-02-08T14:25:31.000Z","updated":"2023-02-09T15:59:57.033Z","comments":true,"path":"2023/02/08/daily/20230208/","link":"","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/2023/02/08/daily/20230208/","excerpt":"","text":"每个人的人性不一样，顺应人性代表的是要顺应不同人不一样的人性，而不是普罗大众的人性。这是今天感悟到的，不用去对任何人好，但是要去研究每一次冲突背后的原因，如何去化解。学习化解冲突的能力和技巧。意识到沟通技巧的重要性。","categories":[{"name":"成长感悟","slug":"成长感悟","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/categories/%E6%88%90%E9%95%BF%E6%84%9F%E6%82%9F/"}],"tags":[{"name":"沟通","slug":"沟通","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E6%B2%9F%E9%80%9A/"},{"name":"人性","slug":"人性","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E4%BA%BA%E6%80%A7/"}]}],"categories":[{"name":"成长感悟","slug":"成长感悟","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/categories/%E6%88%90%E9%95%BF%E6%84%9F%E6%82%9F/"}],"tags":[{"name":"人性","slug":"人性","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E4%BA%BA%E6%80%A7/"},{"name":"朋友","slug":"朋友","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B/"},{"name":"聊天","slug":"聊天","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E8%81%8A%E5%A4%A9/"},{"name":"沙盘演练","slug":"沙盘演练","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E6%B2%99%E7%9B%98%E6%BC%94%E7%BB%83/"},{"name":"上帝视角","slug":"上帝视角","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%9D%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%92/"},{"name":"生产问题","slug":"生产问题","permalink":"http://chenshuohuang.github.io/tags/%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"},{"name":"即兴演讲","slug":"即兴演讲","permalink":"http://chenshuoh